## Code

?<pre class="line-numbers"><code class="language-python">def energy(mass, c=299792458):
    return math.pow(math.mul(mass, c), 2)</code></pre>

## Quote

?<blockquote>
  "Energy cannot be created or destroyed, only transformed."
</blockquote>

